title: The Anadromist: An Invitation
description:
Welcome to The Anadromist. 

This is an invitation to swim against the stream of contemporary life with its addiction to screens, and its political hysteria and mockery. This is the ideas channel for The Anadromous Life. We already have another channel for documents called Gravity From Above. Visit it here!
https://www.youtube.com/user/gulagzero

And our main site for essays which is chock full of provocative content for you. 
https://theanadromist.wordpress.com/

Not to forget our historical and philosophical work on puppetry and other arts at Gravity From Above.
https://gravityfromabove.wordpress.com/

And if you wish to communicate do it over on the Facebook page for The Anadromous Life
https://www.facebook.com/theanadromist/

And finally we aren't using Patreon or any other system at the moment, but we could sure use your help at PayPal. Use this link. 
https://www.paypal.com/donate/?token=i-dCAtFwsmNfdxpJriQal8D6Q5cqi7kXADfqJBvNWXB0EwH9_g8DXzbar75cTnavHqE_cW&country.x=US&locale.x=US
And help me to continue producing The Anadromist.

Let me know what you think over on The Anadromous Life Facebook page. Thanks. Byrne Power 
WELCOME!!!
